General Information

Splenda Granulated low calorie sweetener sweetens everything from beverages, cakes, pies and puddings to breads and muffins

Common Uses

Splenda granulated sweetener has all the sweet taste you want without all of sugars calories, it measures cup for cup and spoon for spoon with sugar.

Ingredients

Maltodextrin, sweetener (sucralose) 1.2%

Directions

see directions on pack or as per recipe
